WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.130 --> 00:00:03.550
Recall that malware is
a malicious program.

00:00:03.550 --> 00:00:07.610
It can spread by various means
from one computer to another.

00:00:07.610 --> 00:00:11.980
And it can perform a wide
variety of malicious activities.

00:00:11.980 --> 00:00:16.740
Up until around early 2000,
although some malware did some damage,

00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:21.250
such as defacing web pages, and some
were launching large scale denial of

00:00:21.250 --> 00:00:25.320
service attacks, The majority
of the malware were designed for

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:28.480
experimenting or
demonstrating some capabilities.

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:33.510
For example, how fast or how large-scale
a malware or worm can spread.

00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:37.430
Therefore, in the era,
the malware was mostly for fun and fame.

